'''Dead trees''' are scenery found in the [[Gravedigger]] random event area. There are 5 trees in the area, as well as one [[Tree stump (Gravedigger)|tree stump]]. They are identical to other [[Dead tree#Big 2|dead trees]] around the world, but cannot be chopped down to obtain logs. Using an axe on them will show {{RSFont|You don't need any wood. What are you planning on doing, making them a fresh coffin?}}
